  "detailed_description": "Rising Runner is a puzzle game for Windows and Linux!<br>Guide Anette Harper through Purgatory, on her quest to reclaim her soul from the Endless Sender.<br><br>Game features:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>16-bit Era style graphics<br></li><li>Rockin' Chiptune Soundtrack By Andy Lemon<br></li><li>Level editor for making custom levels!<br></li><li>Puzzles, action and tension!<br></li><li>All new achievements unique to Steam!<br></li><li>Custom language support(if you wish to translate Rising Runner into your native language)</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Rising Runner is a puzzle game for Windows and Linux!<br>Guide Anette Harper through Purgatory, on her quest to reclaim her soul from the Endless Sender.<br><br>Game features:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>16-bit Era style graphics<br></li><li>Rockin' Chiptune Soundtrack By Andy Lemon<br></li><li>Level editor for making custom levels!<br></li><li>Puzzles, action and tension!<br></li><li>All new achievements unique to Steam!<br></li><li>Custom language support(if you wish to translate Rising Runner into your native language)</li></ul>",
